data.description: DARLING, PULL OVER!! Take a look at this well-maintained remodeled home! This home features an inviting foyer, a spacious living room area, along with a nice-sized kitchen and generously sized bedrooms. It's situated in a prime location and is being offered at a reasonable price. Take advantage of this steal of a deal and schedule your private tour before it's too late!
